\s1 N…ôhap-…ôhap…ôn e nim…ôfak  
\m
\v 1 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n. Nian em…ôtat…®g kitat min it…ômat, okol es…ôghat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat tahmen e net…ômim it…ôm k…®not…ôskas…®k r…ôk…®s e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhalat e Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôp. Em…ôghat k…ôm it…ômat tahmen m…ôm…ô it…ômat net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn …ôm, k…ôn em…ôghat k…ôm it…ômat tahmen m…ôm…ô it…ômat n…®sualk…ôl…ôh …ôm e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn wi r…ôhat…ômat e Kristo.  
\v 2 Nian emat…ôg…ôtun it…ômat, tahmen m…ôm…ô em…ôtagw…ôn it…ômat e melek …ôm, em…ôsos-ip…®n…ô nagw…ôn…ôn …ôskas…®k k…ôm it…ômat m…ôto-inu it…ômat n…ôsotahmen…ôn o nun…ôn.\x - \xo 3:2 \xt Hip 5:12-13; 1 Pita 2:2 \x* K…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn, it…ômat n…ôsotahmen…ôn …ôh o nun…ôn,  
\v 3 m…ôto-inu nol…ôn r…ôhat…ômat tahmen …ôm e r…ôha net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn. Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu it…ômat nakoatetet it…ômat m…®n, k…ôn moat…ôrg…ôh…ôu, k…ôn tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô it…ômat net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn …ôm u. N…ôkotahmen e net…ôm …ôpnap…®n m…®n.\x - \xo 3:3 \xt 1 Kor 1:10-11 \x*  
\v 4 Nian suah kit ot…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo r…ôha Pol,‚Äù k…ôn kit m…®n t…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo r…ôha Apolos,‚Äù nol…ôn …ôh tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô it…ômat net…ôm r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn …ôm.\x - \xo 3:4 \xt 1 Kor 1:12 \x*   
\p
\v 5 Ot…ôplan-tu. ?Apolos in pah, k…ôn Pol in pah? It…®mlau e kuahmen …ôm e iolw…ôk it…ôm emuasitu et…ômat o nuwam…ôn o Iesu. It…®mlau etioal …ôm w…ôk it…ôm I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômos-ipa p…®s…®n p…®s…®n k…ôm it…®mlau m…ôm…ô ekioal.  
\v 6 Tahmen m…ôm…ô io em…ôfe n…®kutin nat, k…ôn Apolos in t…ôtau e n…ôhau, m…ôto Uhg…®n tatol tat…ôwi…ô.\x - \xo 3:6 \xt W…ôk 18:4,11,27-28 \x*  
\v 7 Tol n…ôhlan, et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôfe nat, o et…ôm t…ôtau e n…ôhau, in nat …ôpnap…®n …ôm, m…ôto Uhg…®n p…®s…®n …ôm in nat keike it…ôm tatol nat…®mnat koat…ômeg…ôh moat…ôwi…ô.  
\v 8 Et…ôm tat…ôfe, ne et…ôm t…ôtau, katian …ôm o nat kiti…ôh …ôm. K…ôn Uhg…®n ot…ôtou ilau kiti…ôh kiti…ôh e r…ôhalau w…ôk p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n.  
\v 9 It…®mlau iolw…ôk mil r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn it…ômat n…ôkotahmen e nasum…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, o nim…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 3:9 \xt Mat 16:27; Efes 2:20-22 \x*   
\p
\v 10 E n…ôw…®r…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômawte-in k…ôm io, emil…ôk…®n w…®r nelk…® nim…ô tahmen e et…ôm t…®tun w…®r nil…ôk…®n…ôn nim…ô. K…ôn suah kit m…®n tatil…ôk…®n nim…ô m…ôs…®n. M…ôto ilat rafin okot…ôk…ôike moatehm w…®r w…ôk r…ôhalat r…ôha nil…ôk…®n…ôn nim…ô,  
\v 11 m…ôto-inu okol suah kit t…ôsil…ôk…®n…ôn nelk…® nim…ô kit m…®n it…ôm tol p…®s…®n e inu it…ôm k…®nil…ôk…®n r…ôk…®s. K…ôn nelk…® nim…ô u in Iesu Kristo.\x - \xo 3:11 \xt Aes 28:16; 1 Pita 2:4-6 \x*  
\v 12 Ok…ôm…ô suah kit til…ôk…®n-p…ôr r…ôhan nim…ô it…ôm nelk…® nim…ô in Iesu Kristo, k…ôn in t…®tun nil…ôk…®n…ôn e iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t, o e silfa, o e k…ôpiel n…ômt…®n ti…ôk…®s, o e n…®g, o e nuwig, o e maniah.  
\v 13 K…ôn nian kit net…ômim okot…ôplan w…ôk r…ôhan, m…ôto-inu e nian Iesu tatuwa m…®n, r…ôhan w…ôk otuwa e n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn. R…ôhan w…ôk ok…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn e n…®g…ôm, k…ôn n…®g…ôm ot…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô r…ôhan w…ôk t…ôw…®r or t…ôrat.\x - \xo 3:13 \xt 1 Kor 4:5 \x*  
\v 14 Ok…ôm…ô n…®g…ôm t…ôm…ôsus…ôn r…ôhan nim…ô, in otos r…ôhan n…ôtou…ôn.  
\v 15 M…ôto ok…ôm…ô n…®g…ôm t…ômus r…ôhan nim…ô, k…ôn r…ôhan nat…®mnat rafin t…ôm…®k…ô. In …ôm, Uhg…®n otosmeg…ôh, m…ôto tahmen-ahmen …ôm e suah kit it…ôm taiu m…ôtag…®m e nim…ô it…ôm n…®g…ôm tatus.   
\p
\v 16 ?N…ôkot…®tun o k…ôp m…ôm…ô, it…ômat un nim…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g et…ômat?\x - \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Kor 6:19; 2 Kor 6:16 \x*  
\v 17 Ok…ôm…ô suah kit t…ôr…ôk…®n nim…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn Uhg…®n ot…ôr…ôk…®n in, m…ôto-inu nim…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n, in r…ôhan p…®s…®n …ôm. K…ôn nim…ô u r…ôha Uhg…®n, it…ômat.   
\p
\v 18 T…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô suah kit tateiu…ô-in at…®p in. Ok…ôm…ô suah kit n…®kin t…ôht m…ôm…ô in tenat…®g u-roiu e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ômim, in ot…ôk…ôike muwa ialm…ôl kit e n…®gan…ômt…®lat m…ôm…ô in otuwa ienat…®g pahrien.  
\v 19 Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu nenat…®g…ôn r…ôha net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, in talm…ôl p…®k e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n. Tahmen e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUhg…®n tatol noan…®kulu kit e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha suah kit it…ôm tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in tenat…®g w…®r, k…ôn Uhg…®n task…ôl…®m in.‚Äù\x - \xo 3:19 \xt Job 5:13 \x*  
\v 20 K…ôn Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…®tun m…ôm…ô, n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha net…ôm kotenat…®g, ilat nat …ôpnap…®n …ôm.‚Äù\x - \xo 3:20 \xt Sam 94:11 \x*  
\v 21 K…ôn …ôsot…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômat r…ôha suah u o r…ôha suah …ôh m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr at…®p it…ômat ron. Uhg…®n tatos-ip…ôn nat…®mnat rafin r…ôhat…ômat m…ôm…ô otasitu et…ômat.  
\v 22 Pol, o Apolos, o Pita, o n…ôtueint…ôn, o n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, o n…®m…®s…ôn, o nian roiu, o nian it…ôm tatuwa, ilat rafin r…ôhat…ômat m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otol t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat lan,  
\v 23 k…ôn it…ômat r…ôha Kristo, k…ôn Kristo in r…ôha Uhg…®n.   
\c 4  
\s1 Aposol m…®n r…ôha Kristo  
\m
\v 1 Tol n…ôhlan, net…ômim okot…ôk…ôike motos it…®mat tahmen e iolw…ôk m…®n r…ôha Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn e nelm…®t…®mat m…ôm…ô it…®mat ekotol …ôp nalp…ôkau…ôn anion r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 2 K…ôn net…ômim it…ôm koatehm nat…®mnat r…ôha et…ôm-iasol kit, ilat kot…ôk…ôike motol r…ôhalat w…ôk t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô nian et…ôm-iasol tat…ôplan r…ôhalat w…ôk, k…ôn t…®tun nahat…ôt…ô…ôn elat.\x - \xo 4:2 \xt Luk 12:42 \x*  
\v 3 E io, in nat …ôpnap…®n …ôm ok…ôm…ô it…ômat, o net…ôm p…®s…®n neen kot…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat e r…ôhak w…ôk. K…ôn io at…®p esahmen…ôn o nakil…ôn r…ôhak w…ôk.  
\v 4 E r…ôhak n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn, m…ôm…ô emol …ôm nat it…ôm in t…ôw…®r, m…ôto nat u t…ôs…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô io ek…ôtuat…®p. I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô …ôm t…ôtuat…®p o nakil…ôn r…ôhak w…ôk.  
\v 5 Tol n…ôhlan, sotautaut…ôn o nakil…ôn nat…®mnat. Nakoat…ôsahgin e nian I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô otuwa lan. In ot…ômki-p…ôn e n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn nat…®mnat it…ôm koat…ôhluaig e napin…ôp…ôn, k…ôn in otol-ar…ôp nat naka t…ôtat…®g e n…®ki net…ômim o nol…ôn m…®n r…ôhalat. E nian …ôh Uhg…®n ot…ônwiwi ilat kiti…ôh kiti…ôh.\x - \xo 4:5 \xt 1 Kor 3:8 \x*   
\p
\v 6 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n. Em…ôn-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh k…ôm it…ômat et…®mlau Apolos m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkotos n…®tun…ôn ik…®n, k…ôn ok…ôm…ô nakotos n…®p…ôt…® n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u, ‚ÄúN…ôkot…ôk…ôike motol …ôm n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm k…®n…ôte r…ôk…®s,‚Äù k…ôn n…ôsotos-ip…ôr…ôn net…ôm-iasol neen motos-i…ôhau neen.\x - \xo 4:6 \xt Rom 12:3 \x*  
\v 7 ?Tahro? ?It…ômat il…®s tapr…ôk…®s-in net…ômim m…®n rafin? ?It…ômat nakoatos nat…®mnat neen it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôsos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat? !K…ôp! ?K…ôn tahro nakoat…ôghat ausit o nat…®mnat it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô it…ômat …ôm n…ômotol nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh?\x - \xo 4:7 \xt Rom 12:6 \x*   
\p
\v 8 N…®kit…ômat t…ôhat m…ôm…ô n…®notos rafin r…ôk…®s nat…®mnat r…ôha Uhg…®n. N…®kit…ômat t…ôhat m…ôm…ô n…®notos rafin r…ôk…®s naut…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n. Nol…ôn r…ôhat…ômat tahmen m…ôm…ô n…ômotuwa kig m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n, m…ôto it…®mat ekotat…®g l…ôhau …ôm. !M…ôto k…ôp, s…ôn…ôm…ô n…®pahrien…ôn! !N…ôman! Ok…ôm…ô n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ômotuwa kig m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n, n…®kit…®mat otagien p…®k, k…ôn ok…ôm…ô tol n…ôhlan, it…®mat m…®n ekotol kig kitat min it…ômat. M…ôto t…ôsol…ôn mihin.  
\v 9 It…®mat aposol m…®n, m…ôto n…®kik t…ôht m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu it…®mat …ôp…ôh l…ôhau ag…®n-…ôh, ioatat…®g tahmen e net…ôm it…ôm k…ômakil r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô okot…ôk…ôike mot…®m…®s. N…®kik t…ôht n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu tahmen m…ôm…ô ekoat…ôtul e n…®gan…ômt…® nagelo m…®n ne net…ômim rafin m…ôm…ô ilat okot…ôplan nol…ôn r…ôha n…®m…®s…ôn r…ôhat…®mat.\f + \fr 4:9 \ft Nian kig kit t…ômol win e n…ôluag…®n…ôn, m…®nat…®t…ôl…®g matit r…ôhan mopael m…®n ne r…ôhan t…®k…®m…®r m…®n. R…ôhan mopael m…®n kotuaris…®g-in, k…ôn t…®k…®m…®r m…®n kotuaris…®g-in ilat, k…ôn net…ômim rafin kot…®tun m…ôm…ô t…®k…®m…®r m…®n okot…®m…®s. Net…ômim k…ômotol lafet kit, k…ôn net…ômim rafin koat…ôplan t…®k…®m…®r m…®n at…®p koatoh ilat m…®n, o k…ôm-naka koatol fait ilat nat iarup…®n m…®n tahmen e laion. K…ôn Pol tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in ne r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim kotahmen e t…®k…®m…®r m…®n it…ôm okot…®m…®s, k…ôn net…ômim rafin koat…ôplan. \f*  
\v 10 !Net…ômim tep…ôt koat…ôn m…ôm…ô it…®mat ialm…ôl m…®n o n…ôrg…® Kristo, m…ôto n…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô it…ômat nakotenat…®g w…®r e Kristo! M…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô n…®pahrien…ôn. !Net…ômim tep…ôt koat…ôn m…ôm…ô r…ôhat…®mat nep…ôt…ôn t…®k…ô, m…ôto nakoat…ôghat ausit m…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômat nep…ôt…ôn iahgin! M…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô n…®pahrien…ôn. Net…ômim tep…ôt koat…®siai-in it…ômat, m…ôto kat…ôn rat it…®mat.   
\p
\v 11 M…ôto, inu n…®pahrien…ôn. M…ôtoarus-pa roiu, n…ôum…®s tatus it…®mat, k…ôn moatoaoa, k…ôn ekoatuw…®n e nat…®mnat k…ômot…ôhap-…ôhap, k…ôn net…ômim koatoh it…®mat, k…ôn r…ôhat…®mat nim…ô t…®k…ô.\x - \xo 4:11 \xt 2 Kor 11:23-27 \x*  
\v 12 It…®mat at…®p …ôm ioatol p…®k w…ôk e nelm…®t…®mat. Nian okot…ôn rat it…®mat, m…ôto it…®mat ekot…ôfak o n…ôw…®r…ôn olat. Nian net…ômim koatol n…ôrat…ôn k…ôm it…®mat, m…ôto it…®mat ekot…ôpnap…®n …ôm.\x - \xo 4:12 \xt Mat 5:44; 2 Tes 3:8 \x*  
\v 13 Nian net…ômim koat…ôn rat it…®mat, m…ôto it…®mat ekoat…ôghat w…®r …ôm k…ôm ilat. M…ôtoarus-pa roiu it…®mat ekotahmen e nuwit…®k r…ôha net…ômim rafin, o namk…®m…®k r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn rafin.   
\s1 Ilat okot…ôk…ôike k…ôt…ôu-p…ôn  //  nol…ôn r…ôha Pol  
\p
\v 14 Es…ôte…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u m…ôm…ô ekol it…ômat nakotaul…®s, m…ôto m…ôm…ô ot…ôhgaiir et…ômat, m…ôto-inu it…ômat nen…ôt…®k m…®n it…ôm ekolkeike it…ômat.  
\v 15 R…ôhat…ômat i…ôg…ôtun tep…ôt it…ôm okot…ôg…ôtun it…ômat e Kristo, k…ôn ok…ôm-naka ilat kotahmen …ôm e r…ôhat…ômat tata kal…®n ten-taosan, m…ôto r…ôhat…ômat tata …ôtuat…®p kiti…ôh …ôm, inu io, m…ôto-inu e Kristo Iesu emuwa r…ôhat…ômat tata …ôtuat…®p nian em…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat aup…ôn.\x - \xo 4:15 \xt Kal 4:19 \x*  
\v 16 Tol n…ôhlan, ek…ôtap…ôh …ôskas…®k ot…ômat m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôt…ôu-pa r…ôhak nol…ôn m…®n.\x - \xo 4:16 \xt Fil 3:17 \x*  
\v 17 M…ôto-inu o nat u, etahl-ip…®n…ô n…ôt…®k e Kristo u Timoti it…ôm iakolkeike. In t…ôtaiu …ôskas…®k e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. In ot…ôn m…®n k…ôm it…ômat suat…®p r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhak e Kristo Iesu it…ôm tat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn nat…®mnat it…ôm iat…ôg…ôtun e nim…ôfak m…®n rafin ik…®n m…®n rafin.\x - \xo 4:17 \xt W…ôk 19:22 \x*   
\p
\v 18 It…ômat neen koat…ôn m…ôm…ô es…®mn…ô m…®n…ôn, k…ôn motausit p…®k o r…ôhat…ômat nep…ôt…ôn.  
\v 19 M…ôto ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, ek…ôike m…®mn…ô m…ôplan it…ômat ok…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô teg…ôhan-in io. K…ôn ek…ôs…ôplan …ôm…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm net…ôm iausit m…®n koat…ôn, m…ôto ek…ôplan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôhalat.  
\v 20 M…ôto-inu n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n s…ôn…ôm…ô in nat kit r…ôha n…ôghat…ôn, m…ôto in nat kit r…ôha n…ôsan…ôn…ôn.\x - \xo 4:20 \xt 1 Kor 2:4 \x*  
\v 21 ?K…ôn nakotolkeike naka? ?Ek…®mn…ô malis it…ômat, o ek…®mn…ô e nolkeike…ôn ne narm…®n r…ôha n…ômei…ôn?   
\c 5  
\s1 Pian kit, r…ôhan nol…ôn t…ôrat ag…®n  
\m
\v 1 K…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm io m…ôm…ô suah kit u e n…®kit…ômat t…ôtakl…ôh-in p…ôtan kit, k…ôn t…ômol e nol…ôn t…ôrat kit it…ôm tapr…ôk…®s-in nol…ôn r…ôha net…ôm k…ôsot…ôfak…ôn, nat …ôpnap…®n k…ôsot…ôfak…ôn. In t…ôtakl…ôh-in p…ôtan wi r…ôha r…ôhan tata.\x - \xo 5:1 \xt Lev 18:7-8; Dut 22:30 \x*  
\v 2 !K…ôn it…ômat nakotausit ron m…ôm…ô t…ôw…®r …ôm! N…ôsot…ôto…ôn t…ôrat, m…ôto on…ôkot…ôk…ôike mot…ôto t…ôrat o nol…ôn …ôh, k…ôn n…ôsotahl-iar…ôp…ôn suah …ôh, m…ôto on…ôkot…ôk…ôike motahl-iar…ôp it…ôm t…ômol nol…ôn rat …ôh e n…®kit…ômat.   
\p
\v 3 Nat …ôpnap…®n esat…®g…ôn kitat min it…ômat, m…ôto e narm…®n etat…®g kitat min it…ômat, k…ôn tahmen …ôm ok…ôm…ô kitat koatat…®g, en…ôn r…ôk…®s e n…ôrg…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu m…ôm…ô naka in t…ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô kitat okotol e suah …ôh.\x - \xo 5:3 \xt Kol 2:5 \x*  
\v 4 Nian nakotuwa kiti…ôh, k…ôn e narm…®n, etat…®g kitat min it…ômat, k…ôn nian n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat Iesu in …ôh-ik…®n kitat min,  
\v 5 k…ôn ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôn suah u …ôh-roiu e nelm…® Setan m…ôm…ô ot…ôr…ôk…®n n…®p…ôt…®n, m…ôto I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô otosmeg…ôh narm…®n nian in tatuwa m…®n e namnun nian.\x - \xo 5:5 \xt 1 Tim 1:20 \x*   
\p
\v 6 R…ôhat…ômat nausit…ôn t…ôrat. ?N…ôkot…®tun o k…ôp m…ôm…ô, is noan m…ôs…®n …ôm t…ôtal…ôp…®k api…ôpi…ô flao it…ôm k…ôm…ôt…®g?\x - \xo 5:6 \xt Kal 5:9 \x*  
\v 7 Ot…ôrakin r…ôk…®s is oas m…®n r…ôhat…ômat m…ôm…ô it…ômat flaoa wi it…ôm k…ôm…ôt…®g u is t…®k…ô lan, k…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn it…ômat n…ôkotahmen …ôtuat…®p e p…®ret …ôh. Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu Kristo it…ôm in n…ôt…® sipsip r…ôha lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn, t…ôm…®m…®s r…ôk…®s tahmen e sakrifais o nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhatat.\x - \xo 5:7 \xt Aes 53:7; 1 Pita 1:19 \x*  
\v 8 Tol n…ôhlan, p…ôs kotol lafet …ôh, m…ôto k…ôsotol…ôn e is oas, it…ôm tahmen e nol…ôn t…ôrat m…®n it…ôm net…ômim kotolkeike p…®k nol…ôn k…ôm net…ômim, ne nol…ôn rat m…®n rafin. M…ôto p…ôs kotol lafet e P…®ret U Is T…®k…ô Lan, tahmen e nol…ôn rafin it…ôm kotol n…®pahrien…ôn mot…ôtuat…®p.\x - \xo 5:8 \xt Dut 16:3 \x*   
\p
\v 9 Em…ôte r…ôk…®s naoa k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô n…ôsotan k…ôl…ôh…ôn it…ômat net…ôm koatakl…ôh-in p…ôtan.  
