\v 1 K…ôn roiu, iak…ôghat e nagw…ôn…ôn m…®n it…ôm katol-p…ôn sakrifais lan k…ôm narm…® nat m…®n. Kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô, ‚Äúkitat rafin koatos n…®tun…ôn.‚Äù ‚ÄúN…®tun…ôn‚Äù in nat kit it…ôm suah kit t…ôtausit ron, m…ôto nolkeike…ôn tatil…ôk…®n mat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr et…ômim.\x - \xo 8:1 \xt W…ôk 15:29 \x*  
