\m
\v 1 ?N…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô ek…®tun nol…ôn nat naka it…ôm iakolkeike, o k…ôp? !∆èw…ôh! ?Io aposol kit, o k…ôp? !∆èw…ôh! ?Em…ôplan Iesu I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat e n…®gan…ômt…ôk, o k…ôp? !∆èw…ôh! ?It…ômat u noa r…ôhak w…ôk e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, o k…ôp? !∆èw…ôh!\x - \xo 9:1 \xt W…ôk 22:17-18; 26:16; 1 Kor 15:8-9 \x*  
\v 2 Ok…ôm…ô net…ômim neen koat…ôn m…ôm…ô s…ôn…ôm…ô io aposol, m…ôto n…®pahrien…ôn, it…ômat n…ôsot…®tun n…ôn…ôn n…ôhlan, m…ôto-inu n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô io aposol kit.\x - \xo 9:2 \xt 2 Kor 3:2-3 \x*   
