\v 5 Aposol m…®n neen, ne pia I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô m…®n, ne Pita,\f + \fr 9:5 \ft N…ôghat…ôn Kris …ôtuat…®p tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄòKefas‚Äô it…ôm in n…ôrg…®n kit m…®n r…ôha Pita\f* r…ôhalat n…®p…®tan it…ôm koat…ôfak koatuaris…®g-in ilat nian ilat kotaliw…ôk moatol w…ôk r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. ?In t…ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô kitat kotol tahmen-ahmen …ôm, o k…ôp? ∆èw…ôh, it…ômat n…ôkot…®tun.  
\v 6 ?O n…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô io …ôm ne Panapas, it…®mlau p…®s…®n …ôm eku…ôk…ôike mioal at…®p w…ôk o nat…®g…ôn r…ôhat…®mlau?   
