\v 17 Ok…ôm…ô iat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôto-inu iakolkeike mol nulan, k…ôn t…ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô ekos n…ôtou…ôn lan. M…ôto in Uhg…®n …ôm it…ôm t…ôm…®t…ôpun io m…ôm…ô ekol w…ôk u, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, ek…ôike mol.  
\v 18 ?K…ôn r…ôhak n…ôtou…ôn in naka? In …ôm u, m…ôm…ô nian ek…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r, ek…ôn-iar…ôp …ôpnap…®n …ôm, m…ôsos…ôn n…ôtou…ôn lan, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan es…ôtap…ôh…ôn o nat kit, nat …ôpnap…®n in t…ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô ekol.   
\p
\v 19 Suah kit t…ôs…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn lak, m…ôto io emos-i…ôhau at…®p io m…ôm…ô io slef …ôm r…ôha net…ômim rafin m…ôm…ô ekiuw-pa tep…ôt kotuwa o Kristo.  
\v 20 Nian em…ôtan it…®mat net…ôm Isrel, emuwa mahmen e net…ôm Isrel m…ôm…ô ekiuw-pa ilat kotuwa o Kristo. K…ôn nat …ôpnap…®n Lou t…ôs…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn lak, nian em…ôtan it…®mat net…ôm koat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn Lou, emuwa mahmen elat, m…ôm…ô ekiuw-pa ilat kotuwa o Kristo.\x - \xo 9:20 \xt W…ôk 21:20-26 \x*  
\v 21 Nian em…ôtan it…®mat net…ôm k…ôsot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn Lou, emuwa mahmen elat. M…ôto es…ôrakin…ôn lou r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôp. Lou r…ôha Kristo tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô lak. Emol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô ekiuw-pa ilat kotuwa o Kristo.  
