\v 23 Iatol n…ôhlan o namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô io m…®n ekos nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n r…ôhan.   
\p
\v 24 ?N…ôkot…®tun o k…ôp m…ôm…ô, e naiu…ôn, net…ômim rafin koataiu, m…ôto kiti…ôh …ôm tatol win? K…ôn t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô nakotaiu e nol…ôn r…ôha naiu…ôn it…ôm nakotalkut p…®k m…ôm…ô on…ôkotol win.\fig |alt="man wearing wreath" src="BK00157B.TIF" size="col" loc="1Co 9:24-27" ref="1 Kor 9:24" \fig*  
