\v 26 Tol n…ôhlan, tahmen e naiu…ôn, esaiu …ôpnap…®n…ôn, k…ôn tahmen e boksig, es…ôht-ar…ôp…ôn…ôn tahmen e et…ômim tat…ôht magoag…ôp.  
\v 27 !K…ôp! Iat…ôtuak…ôm k…ôm n…®p…ôt…®k m…ôm…ô otuwa r…ôhak slef. Iatol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô, nian em…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm net…ômim tep…ôt r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô ilat okotuwa e naiu…ôn …ôh, k…ôn io ek…ôsuwam…ôn mahmen e et…ômim it…ôm t…ôm…ôtg…ôhl lou r…ôha naiu…ôn k…ôn k…ôrakin e naiu…ôn.\x - \xo 9:27 \xt Rom 8:13; 13:14 \x*   
\c 10  
\s1 Pol t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp nol…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel aup…ôn  
\m
\v 1 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n, iakolkeike m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô nian t…®p…®t…®mat m…®n k…ômotiet Ijip, ilat rafin, mal napu…ô t…ôm…ôtag…ôhl olat,\x - \xo 10:1 \xt Eks 13:21-22\x* k…ôn ilat rafin k…ômotuw…®n-p…ôn it…ôh…ôi u kat…ôn m…ôm…ô N…®t…ôh…ôi Asi…ô.\x - \xo 10:1 \xt Eks 14:22\x*  
\v 2 K…ôn e mal napu…ô ne n…®t…ôh…ôi, Uhg…®n t…ômol baptais elat rafin m…ôm…ô okotuwa net…ômim r…ôha Moses.  
