\v 4 k…ôn mot…ôn…®m n…ôhau kiti…ôh …ôm it…ôm t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, m…ôto-inu k…ômot…ôn…®m n…ôhau e k…ôpiel r…ôha Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ôm…ôtan ilat min ilat,\x - \xo 10:4 \xt Eks 17:6; Nam 20:11\x* k…ôn k…ôpiel …ôh in Kristo.  
\v 5 Nat …ôpnap…®n ilat k…ômotol n…ôhlan, m…ôto Uhg…®n n…®kin t…ôm…ôsagien…ôn olat tep…ôt, k…ôn ilat tep…ôt k…ômot…®m…®s …ôp…ôh ik…®n p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n.\x - \xo 10:5 \xt Nam 14:29-30\x*   
\p
\v 6 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômeg…ôhan-in nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh m…ôm…ô ilat n…ômt…ôtin m…®n m…ôm…ô ot…ôhgaiir etat mot…ôg…ôtun itat, k…ôn ok…ôsotol…ôn t…®k…®r…®lat mot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôhatat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn e nol…ôn rat m…®n tahmen e it…ôm k…ômotol aup…ôn.\x - \xo 10:6 \xt Nam 11:4,34; 1 Kor 10:11 \x*  
\v 7 ∆èsot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn nol…ôn r…ôha n…ôfak…ôn k…ôm narm…® nat m…®n tahmen elat neen k…ômoatol aup…ôn. Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNet…ômim k…ômot…ôp…ôl…ôh m…ôm…ô okotagw…ôn mot…ôn…®m, k…ôn mot…ôtul m…ôm…ô okotol danis u tiuw-p…ôn ilat t…ôrat ik…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 10:7 \xt Eks 32:4,6,19\x*  
\v 8 T…ôrat m…ôm…ô kitat okotit anion n…®p…®tan tahmen elat neen k…ômoatol aup…ôn, k…ôn ilat rafin tuente-tri-taosan k…ômot…®m…®s e nian kiti…ôh …ôm.\x - \xo 10:8 \xt Nam 25:1-9\x*  
\v 9 T…ôrat m…ôm…ô kitat okotol nat…®mnat it…ôm otiuw nem…ôha r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô\f + \fr 10:9 \ft Tat…ôghat o nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim it…ôm koatol nol…ôn rat kit, k…ôn nol…ôn rat kit m…®n, tatuw…®n matuw…®n m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan ok…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otol nalp…®n…ôn o k…ôp.\f* \x - \xo 10:9 \xt Eks 17:2\x* tahmen elat neen k…ômoatol aup…ôn, k…ôn s…®nek tus ilat kot…®m…®s.\x - \xo 10:9 \xt Nam 21:5,6\x*  
\v 10 T…ôrat m…ôm…ô nakot…ôn n…®kal…® Uhg…®n tahmen elat neen k…ômoatol aup…ôn,\x - \xo 10:10 \xt Nam 16:41-50; 17:5,10\x* k…ôn nagelo r…ôha n…®m…®s…ôn tohamnu ilat.   
\p
\v 11 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômeg…ôhan-in nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh m…ôm…ô otuwa e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhalat, m…ôm…ô ilat n…ômt…ôtin m…®n, k…ôn k…ôm…ôte ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôhgaiir etat mot…ôg…ôtun itat, it…ôm koatat…®g roiu m…ôm…ô namnun nian tatuwa iu…ôhk…®r.  
\v 12 K…ôn ok…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô nakot…ôtul …ôskas…®k, oat…ôto w…®r it…ômat, m…ôto-inu it…ômat m…®n n…ôkot…®tun n…ôme…ôn e nol…ôn rat m…®n …ôh.  
\v 13 Nos-ip…ôn-os-ip…ôn…ôn it…ôm tatuwa e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat tahmen …ôm e it…ôm katol mihin e net…ômim rafin. M…ôto nian rafin, Uhg…®n tatol r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn ot…ôseg…ôhan-in…ôn nos-ip…ôn-os-ip…ôn…ôn otuwa e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat m…ôm…ô in t…ôskas…®k mapr…ôk…®s-in n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôhat…ômat. M…ôto nian nos-ip…ôn-os-ip…ôn…ôn tatuwa e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, Uhg…®n otol suat…®p kit m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…®tun nos…ôn n…ôtul…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, m…ôm…ô nat …ôh ot…ôsiuw-p…ôn…ôn it…ômat e n…ôrat…ôn.   
\s1 Narm…® nat m…®n ne i…ôfak m…®n  
\p
