\v 15 It…ômat net…ôm kotenat…®g, k…ôn otakil at…®p n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhak m…ôm…ô in t…ôw…®r o t…ôrat.  
\v 16 Nian kitat kotagwen e Nagw…ôn…ôn R…ôha N…ômt…ôtin R…ôha Iesu, k…ôn mot…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô n…®kitat tagien o n…ôn…®m…ôn, k…ôn moat…ôn…®m n…ôn…®m…ôn …ôh, tahmen m…ôm…ô kitat koatuwa moatol kiti…ôh kitat Kristo e n…®tan. ?Iat…ôn pahrien, o k…ôp? K…ôn nian kitat koatun p…®ret it…ôm kot…ômkas katoor, kitat koatuwa kiti…ôh kitat Kristo. ?Iat…ôn pahrien, o k…ôp?\x - \xo 10:16 \xt Mat 26:26-28 \x*  
\v 17 Kitat u net…ômim tep…ôt, m…ôto kotahmen e n…®p…ôt…®n kiti…ôh …ôm, m…ôto-inu p…®ret kiti…ôh …ôm, k…ôn kitat rafin koatun …ôm p…®ret …ôh.\x - \xo 10:17 \xt Rom 12:5 \x*   
\p
\v 18 N…®kit…ômat tat…ôht nol…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel. Nian et…ôm tatol sakrifais k…ôm Uhg…®n, k…ôn net…ômim neen koatun mit it…ôm k…ômol sakrifais lan, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô ilat rafin k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh ilat Uhg…®n e sakrifais …ôh. ?Inu n…®pahrien…ôn, o k…ôp? ∆èw…ôh, in n…®pahrien…ôn.\x - \xo 10:18 \xt Lev 7:6 \x*   
\p
\v 19 ?Naka n…®p…ôt…® r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn m…®n? ?Tahro? ?Iakat…ôn m…ôm…ô mit it…ôm katol sakrifais lan k…ôm narm…® nat m…®n n…ôsan…ôn…ôn …ôh-ik…®n r…ôhalat, o k…ôp? K…ôp. ?O tahro? ?Iakat…ôn m…ôm…ô narm…® nat m…®n, ilat uhg…®n …ôlk…ôl…ôh m…®n neen, o k…ôp? K…ôp.\x - \xo 10:19 \xt 1 Kor 8:4 \x*  
\v 20 M…ôto iakat…ôn m…ôm…ô nian net…ômim koatol sakrifais k…ôm narm…® nat m…®n, koatol k…ôm i…ôrm…®s m…®n, k…ôsotol…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n. K…ôn esolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô nakotuwa kiti…ôh it…ômat i…ôrm…®s m…®n.\x - \xo 10:20 \xt Dut 32:17; Nol ∆èp…ôn 9:20 \x*  
\v 21 Okol n…ôsuw…®n…ôn mun p…®ret ne wain e Nagw…ôn…ôn R…ôha N…ômt…ôtin R…ôha Iesu, k…ôn mat…®g muw…®n m…®n e nim…ôfak r…ôha narm…® nat m…®n mun sakrifais ne wain r…ôha i…ôrm…®s m…®n ilat net…ôm koat…ôfak lan.\x - \xo 10:21 \xt 2 Kor 6:15-16 \x*  
\v 22 ?Tahro? ?N…ôkoatol m…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô otetet it…ômat tahmen e net…ôm Isrel? ?N…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôhatat tep…ôt mapr…ôk…®s-in r…ôha Uhg…®n?\x - \xo 10:22 \xt Dut 32:21 \x*   
\p
\v 23 It…ômat nakoat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúT…ôw…®r …ôm m…ôm…ô ekol nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm iakolkeike.‚Äù M…ôto io ek…ôn m…ôm…ô, s…ôn…ôm…ô ilat rafin koatasitu et…ômat. It…ômat nakoat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúT…ôw…®r …ôm m…ôm…ô ekol nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm iakolkeike.‚Äù M…ôto io ek…ôn m…ôm…ô s…ôn…ôm…ô ilat rafin it…ôm koatasitu e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat.\x - \xo 10:23 \xt 1 Kor 6:12 \x*  
\v 24 T…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômat kit tateg…ôs-in at…®p r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn, m…ôto tat…ôk…ôike meg…ôs-in m…®n r…ôha net…ômim m…®n neen.\x - \xo 10:24 \xt Rom 15:1-2 \x*   
\p
